translations.title: Modern Hanging Kitchen Utensil Rack with Bowl
translations.description: Elegant and space-saving wall-mounted utensil organizer crafted from natural bamboo/wood with a minimalist frame design.

translations.title: رف أدوات مطبخ معلق حديث مع وعاء
translations.description: منظم أدوات مطبخ أنيق وموفر للمساحة مثبت على الحائط، مصنوع من الخيزران/الخشب الطبيعي بتصميم إطار بسيط.

images.alt: Modern wall-mounted kitchen utensil rack in natural wood with white bowl on top and hanging black matte and wooden spoons & ladles
Close-up of minimalist bamboo utensil holder displaying mixed black and natural wood cooking spoons and ladles with ceramic bowl
Close-up of minimalist bamboo utensil holder displaying mixed black and natural wood cooking spoons and ladles with ceramic bowl

translations.title: Stainless Steel Utensil Rack
translations.description: Durable stainless steel wall-mounted rack with hooks for organizing kitchen tools. Features a sleek, rust-resistant design perfect for modern kitchens.

translations.title: رف أدوات مطبخ من الفولاذ المقاوم للصدأ
translations.description: رف متين مثبت على الحائط من الفولاذ المقاوم للصدأ مع خطافات لتنظيم أدوات المطبخ. يتميز بتصميم أنيق مقاوم للصدأ مثالي للمطابخ الحديثة.

images.alt: Stainless steel wall-mounted kitchen utensil rack with hooks for spoons and ladles
Close-up of stainless steel utensil holder displaying various cooking utensils
Detailed view of stainless steel utensil rack with organized tools

translations.title: Wooden Countertop Utensil Holder
translations.description: Compact wooden countertop organizer with multiple compartments for spoons, spatulas, and more. Made from sustainable wood for a rustic kitchen aesthetic.

translations.title: حامل أدوات مطبخ خشبي للمنضدة
translations.description: منظم مضغوط للمنضدة من الخشب مع حجرات متعددة للمعالق والملاعق وغيرها. مصنوع من خشب مستدام لمظهر ريفي أنيق في المطبخ.

images.alt: Wooden countertop kitchen utensil holder with compartments for tools
Close-up of wooden utensil organizer displaying mixed kitchen utensils
Detailed view of wooden utensil holder with organized compartments

translations.title: Magnetic Knife and Utensil Rack
translations.description: Magnetic wall rack for knives and metal utensils, keeping them secure and accessible. Includes a non-slip base for added stability in busy kitchens.

translations.title: رف مغناطيسي للسكاكين وأدوات المطبخ
translations.description: رف حائط مغناطيسي للسكاكين والأدوات المعدنية، يحافظ عليها آمنة وسهلة الوصول. يتضمن قاعدة مانعة للانزلاق لثبات إضافي في المطابخ المزدحمة.

images.alt: Magnetic wall-mounted kitchen utensil rack for knives and tools
Close-up of magnetic utensil holder displaying knives and metal spoons
Detailed view of magnetic utensil rack with secured utensils

translations.title: Ceramic Utensil Caddy
translations.description: Elegant ceramic caddy with divided sections for organizing utensils. Features a glazed finish that's easy to clean and adds charm to your countertop.

translations.title: حامل أدوات سيراميك
translations.description: حامل سيراميك أنيق مع أقسام مقسمة لتنظيم الأدوات. يتميز بطبقة زجاجية سهلة التنظيف ويضيف سحرًا لمنضدة المطبخ.

images.alt: Ceramic countertop kitchen utensil caddy with divided sections
Close-up of ceramic utensil organizer displaying various tools
Detailed view of ceramic utensil caddy with organized compartments

translations.title: Expandable Utensil Rack
translations.description: Versatile expandable wall rack that adjusts to fit your space. Crafted from metal with hooks for hanging utensils, ideal for small or large kitchens.

translations.title: رف أدوات قابل للتمدد
translations.description: رف حائط متعدد الاستخدامات قابل للتمدد يتكيف مع مساحتك. مصنوع من المعدن مع خطافات لتعليق الأدوات، مثالي للمطابخ الصغيرة والكبيرة.

images.alt: Expandable wall-mounted kitchen utensil rack with adjustable hooks
Close-up of expandable utensil holder displaying hanging tools
Detailed view of expandable utensil rack in extended position

translations.title: Bamboo Utensil Organizer
translations.description: Eco-friendly bamboo organizer with tiered shelves for utensils. Lightweight and sturdy, perfect for keeping your kitchen essentials neatly arranged.

translations.title: منظم أدوات خيزران
translations.description: منظم صديق للبيئة من الخيزران مع أرفف متدرجة للأدوات. خفيف الوزن وقوي، مثالي للحفاظ على أساسيات المطبخ مرتبة بشكل أنيق.

images.alt: Bamboo countertop kitchen utensil organizer with tiered shelves
Close-up of bamboo utensil holder displaying organized tools
Detailed view of bamboo utensil organizer with shelves

translations.title: Over-the-Cabinet Utensil Rack
translations.description: Space-efficient over-the-cabinet rack with rails for hanging utensils. Made from durable plastic, easy to install and maintain in any kitchen.

translations.title: رف أدوات فوق الخزانة
translations.description: رف موفر للمساحة يثبت فوق الخزانة مع قضبان لتعليق الأدوات. مصنوع من بلاستيك متين، سهل التركيب والصيانة في أي مطبخ.

images.alt: Over-the-cabinet kitchen utensil rack with hanging rails
Close-up of over-the-cabinet utensil holder displaying tools
Detailed view of over-the-cabinet utensil rack installed

translations.title: Rotating Utensil Stand
translations.description: Rotating countertop stand with multiple levels for easy access to utensils. Features a 360-degree turntable for convenience in compact spaces.

translations.title: حامل أدوات دوّار
translations.description: حامل منضدة دوّار بمستويات متعددة لسهولة الوصول إلى الأدوات. يتميز بقرص دوّار 360 درجة للراحة في المساحات المدمجة.

images.alt: Rotating countertop kitchen utensil stand with multiple levels
Close-up of rotating utensil holder displaying organized tools
Detailed view of rotating utensil stand in motion

translations.title: Wire Mesh Utensil Rack
translations.description: Industrial-style wire mesh rack for wall mounting utensils. Provides excellent ventilation and a modern look for contemporary kitchens.

translations.title: رف أدوات شبكي معدني
translations.description: رف شبكي معدني بأسلوب صناعي لتثبيت الأدوات على الحائط. يوفر تهوية ممتازة ومظهرًا عصريًا للمطابخ المعاصرة.

images.alt: Wire mesh wall-mounted kitchen utensil rack
Close-up of wire mesh utensil holder displaying tools
Detailed view of wire mesh utensil rack with hanging utensils

translations.title: Tiered Utensil Rack
translations.description: Multi-tiered rack for countertop use, with shelves for different utensil sizes. Made from chrome-plated metal for durability and style.

translations.title: رف أدوات متعدد الطبقات
translations.description: رف متعدد الطبقات للاستخدام على المنضدة، مع أرفف لأحجام مختلفة من الأدوات. مصنوع من معدن مطلي بالكروم للمتانة والأناقة.

images.alt: Tiered countertop kitchen utensil rack with multiple shelves
Close-up of tiered utensil holder displaying organized tools
Detailed view of tiered utensil rack with shelves

translations.title: Compact Drawer Utensil Organizer
translations.description: Compact organizer designed for kitchen drawers, with adjustable dividers. Keeps utensils sorted and easily accessible in limited space.

translations.title: منظم أدوات درج مطبخ مدمج
translations.description: منظم مدمج مصمم لأدراج المطبخ مع فواصل قابلة للتعديل. يحافظ على ترتيب الأدوات وسهولة الوصول إليها في مساحة محدودة.

images.alt: Compact drawer kitchen utensil organizer with adjustable dividers
Close-up of drawer utensil organizer displaying sorted tools
Detailed view of compact utensil organizer in a drawer
